library(ggplot2)
library(cowplot)

a = ggplot(dataSet)+
  geom_histogram(aes(dataSet$Length),fill="#00a86b")+
  labs(title = "Distribution of Length",x = "Length",y = "Frequency")+
  theme(axis.title = element_text(face = "bold"),plot.title = element_text(face = "bold",size = 16))

b = ggplot(dataSet)+
